OL,3,CGovernment's #200 million software
OL,4,Cdeal 'totally inadequate'
OL,6,FA #200 million contract between
OL,7,FGuernsey's government and a software
OL,8,Fcompany has been said to be "totally
OL,9,Finadequate" with "serious mistakes
OL,10,Fmade", a new report has found.
OL,12,FLeadership, strategy, investment,
OL,13,Fexpert advice, and management were all
OL,14,Fsaid to have been lacking, according
OL,15,Fto a scrutiny panel.
OL,17,FIn 2019, the States signed a 10-year
OL,18,Fpartnership with Agilisys Limited to
OL,19,Fmodernise IT systems and deliver
OL,20,Fdigital public services.
