OL,6,FIn November of that year, Agilisys
OL,7,Ftook on responsibility for the
OL,8,Fmanagement and ongoing development of
OL,9,Fmost of the States of Guernsey's IT
OL,10,Fsystems under a programme called
OL,11,F'Future Digital Services.'
OL,13,FIt set Agilisys up as the Government's
OL,14,FIT partner, with big plans to overhaul
OL,15,FStates' systems.
