OL,3,CGovernment's #200 million software
OL,4,Cdeal 'totally inadequate'
OL,6,FHowever, there were major issues and a
OL,7,Fdetailed review started in 2022 to
OL,8,Fidentify its value for money, the
OL,9,Fprogress made in digital
OL,10,Ftransformation, and contract
OL,11,Fmanagement, among other measures.
OL,13,FFollowing this damning report, former
OL,14,FPolicy and Resources member Deputy
OL,15,FMark Helyar says senior government
OL,16,Fofficials should be sacked.
