OL,6,FAgilisys has said it will support the
OL,7,Fappointment of an advisory board with
OL,8,FIT industry expertise to help
OL,9,Fpoliticians make strategic IT
OL,10,Fdecisions.
OL,12,FAndrew Mindenhall, CEO of Agilisys,
OL,13,Fsays: "I would like to acknowledge the
OL,14,Ftenacity and commitment of all the
OL,15,Findividuals across the partnership who
OL,16,Fhave been pivotal in delivering the
OL,17,Fchanges identified, as well as the
OL,18,Fprofessionalism and resilience shown
OL,19,Fin sometimes challenging situations.
